	- Fix that formerrors are ratelimited.

19 May 2015: Wouter
	- max-interfaces raised to 32.

18 May 2015: Wouter
	- removed unused defines for unofficial tsig-hmac algorithm codes.
	  The TSIG algorithm is identified by name in the config file.

